| location_id          | bigint(20)    | NO   | PRI | NULL    |       |
| schema_version       | bigint(20)    | NO   | PRI | NULL    |       |
| gmt_create           | timestamp(6)  | NO   |     | NULL    |       |
| gmt_modified         | timestamp(6)  | NO   |     | NULL    |       |
| is_deleted           | bigint(20)    | NO   |     | NULL    |       |
| location_name        | varchar(128)  | YES  |     |         |       |
| location_url         | varchar(4000) | YES  |     |         |       |
| location_access_info | varchar(8000) | YES  |     |         |       |
+----------------------+---------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
